Package UserCode.Factory

Interface Summary
IComponentFactory IComponentFactory defines the behaviour a concrete class that creates IComponent's should implement.
IEntityCreatorFactory IEntityCreatorFactory defines the behaviour a concrete implementation should include that creates and returns IEntity's
IManagerFactory IManagerCreator defines the Interface of a class that creates top level managers required in an aquarium simulation
ITokenFactory ITokenFactory defines the Interface of a factory that should return an IToken based on the String provided
 

Class Summary
ComponentFactory ComponentFactory defines the behaviour of the concrete implementation of the IComponentFactory interface.
ComponentFactoryTest The test class ComponentFactoryTest for testing the ComponentFactory production class.
EntityCreatorFactory EntityCreatorFactory: A factory to create the different types of pets that can be used within the aquarium.
EntityCreatorFactoryTest The test class EntityCreatorFactoryTest, used to test the EntitiyCreatorFactory.
ManagerFactory ManagerCreator defines the class that creates all the top level managers required for the aquarium simulation
ManagerFactoryTest The test class ManagerCreatorTest for testing the production class ManagerCreator.
TokenFactory TokenFactory defines the behaviour of a factory that creates and returns an IToken with an image based on the String value passed, the implementation of the ITokenFactory
TokenFactoryTest The test class TokenFactoryTest for testing the production class TokenFactory.
